comments.body:
This error is the result of Blizzard's buggy taint catcher. It picks an addon at random blame for this error, even though that addon has done nothing wrong. I have personally seen this error happen with TellMeWhen as well as half of the other addons that I use. There is nothing that I can do about it because there is nothing in TellMeWhen's code that would be triggering this.
